{"tid":968081,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]未割包皮嘅你，屙尿會唔會反開包皮？","createTime":"2019-01-04T03:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T15:48:27.000Z","uid":40757,"like":290,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"83704fed78f91ca17a7a2da504bf8b51c6b38252","tid":968081,"uid":40757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T03:09:22.000Z","msg":"不嬲由細到大都係反開包皮先屙<br />\n唔反包皮就咁屙<br />\n一黎難控制方向，易屙出界<br />\n二黎好似屙落塊包皮到，成塊都係尿，諗起都覺得核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但自從有次俾個fd話我屙得太大力<br />\n啲尿反彈落佢隻腳之後<br />\n我屙尿嘅時候觀察到<br />\n好幾個朋友都係唔反包皮就咁屙落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問返佢地點解唔反包皮就咁屙<br />\n俾佢地反問返我點解要反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n究竟各位平時係反左先屙定係就咁屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n示意圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YjfJnSA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYjfJnSA.png&h=079c37e3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NpyiWcH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNpyiWcH.png&h=4ed188e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f65c2aae72d2717c376ce0950e91444377143f8","tid":968081,"uid":38434,"like":109,"dislike":5,"score":104,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T03:10:08.000Z","msg":"反"},{"pid":"7cb1595caeaca5d20d7ea428ed10c7c98730d696","tid":968081,"uid":19712,"like":67,"dislike":4,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T03:10:42.000Z","msg":"因為佢地係處男"},{"pid":"c65d8d7945cf6f57c1df29b93d8ec07a208ad757","tid":968081,"uid":40757,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"7cb1595caeaca5d20d7ea428ed10c7c98730d696","tid":968081,"uid":19712,"like":67,"dislike":4,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T03:10:42.000Z","msg":"因為佢地係處男"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T03:11:28.000Z","msg":"有個唔係處都冇反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":